*.env*
# The template carries no secrets and is what the README tells you to copy.
!.env.example
# The Capacitor build's API origin. No secrets, and it MUST be committed: without it a CI build
# silently produces a bundle with an empty VITE_API_BASE, which makes the app call itself instead
# of the API — sign-in then hangs on the login screen with no error.
!web/.env.app
deploy.bat
node_modules/
dist/
dev-dist/
*.ps1
codebase.md